{"tid":991103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"威院肺癌病人剪刀自插身亡","createTime":"2019-01-22T06:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T05:55:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":104,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"78cd227a7e073b2d354ff13fd4efac7436579f45","tid":991103,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:31:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190122/20596543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F20596543&d=eHGin6srybVV6v6u95%2FlFzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=76bb6330\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F20596543&h=6c877cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190122/20596543</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月22日 <br />\n<br />\n威院肺癌病人剪刀自插身亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190122/large/22la4p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190122%2Flarge%2F22la4p10.jpg&h=2757c2de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n威爾斯親王醫院一名男病人自殺身亡，院方將個案呈報死因裁判官跟進。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙田威爾斯親王醫院發生病人自殺身亡事件。一名40歲男病人因為氣促，上周六由沙田醫院轉到威院外科病房，同日接受支氣管內窺鏡檢查。惟檢查後約一小時，醫生發現病人已失去意識，心跳停頓，床邊留有一把染血剪刀及遺書。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自行攜帶剪刀<br />\n<br />\n醫生搶救發現病人左胸有四處傷口，院方即時通知病人家屬並報警，病人延至當晚11時39分離世。威院發言人表示，個案已呈報死因裁判官跟進。據悉，該把剪刀是病人自行攜帶，並非在醫院拿取。<br />\n<br />\n由於當日病人早已換上病人服，故剪刀較大可能放在隨身行李。該名病人患嚴重肺癌，已在沙田醫院療養一段時間，當日因氣促，轉到威院接受內窺鏡檢查。遺書透露死者因為患病，非常辛苦，故有尋死意向。醫院指對事件感到非常難過，會為家屬提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n急症科醫學院院長蕭粵中表示，左胸是心臟、肺部所在，亦有多條動脈，若遭刺傷，可導致大量出血、心臟短時間內停頓、血胸等嚴重症狀。<br />\n<br />\n他指即使病人在病房內接駁了維生指數監測儀器，在出現嚴重創傷的初期，儀器未必即時發出聲響，要等到脈搏、血壓有較明顯變化時才發聲，故忙於工作的醫護，或未必立即察覺到病人自殘。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民、何家朗  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n路線建議不清晰　運署被轟<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n赴台做咖啡店女僕　港女被捕"},{"pid":"b5d4d36f050056fa09297c18c42a8484fd3646ed","tid":991103,"uid":65201,"like":21,"dislike":482,"score":-461,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:33:30.000Z","msg":"醫護狗仲覺得自己好撚盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba30d7c9b6d8b6f7c4c017b58cbb5466f267149d","tid":991103,"uid":61748,"like":18,"dislike":292,"score":-274,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dd7952eda69a40a110c61836b19a3833a4cfb03","tid":991103,"uid":193984,"like":430,"dislike":3,"score":427,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"好大勇氣...一定辛苦到有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a68bf2aba381761d41febe8f0f25bfd06a2ed0","tid":991103,"uid":51701,"like":172,"dislike":1,"score":171,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"咁死好辛苦<br />\n肺充血又缺氧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0727f481323c3f3efb31b3a1526e33f8830fc4","tid":991103,"uid":52911,"like":295,"dislike":5,"score":290,"quote":{"pid":"b5d4d36f050056fa09297c18c42a8484fd3646ed","tid":991103,"uid":65201,"like":21,"dislike":482,"score":-461,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:33:30.000Z","msg":"醫護狗仲覺得自己好撚盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"你覺得如果1:6 定1:15 發生呢啲事機會大啲？"},{"pid":"852f4981d1171812f11b52b868afd84911eef75e","tid":991103,"uid":156376,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"54a68bf2aba381761d41febe8f0f25bfd06a2ed0","tid":991103,"uid":51701,"like":172,"dislike":1,"score":171,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"咁死好辛苦<br />\n肺充血又缺氧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime