":"40歲就有肺癌仲要末期<br />\n<br />\n有可能係死煙產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煙產知道自己下場未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5399fd5903973f830932886940c9464983254aba","tid":991103,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc3922826676b7d52c34be5e8f8fde80bb2bf121","tid":991103,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78cd227a7e073b2d354ff13fd4efac7436579f45","tid":991103,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:31:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190122/20596543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F20596543&d=eHGin6srybVV6v6u95%2FlFzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=76bb6330\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F20596543&h=6c877cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190122/20596543</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月22日 <br />\n<br />\n威院肺癌病人剪刀自插身亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190122/large/22la4p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190122%2Flarge%2F22la4p10.jpg&h=2757c2de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n威爾斯親王醫院一名男病人自殺身亡，院方將個案呈報死因裁判官跟進。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙田威爾斯親王醫院發生病人自殺身亡事件。一名40歲男病人因為氣促，上周六由沙田醫院轉到威院外科病房，同日接受支氣管內窺鏡檢查。惟檢查後約一小時，醫生發現病人已失去意識，心跳停頓，床邊留有一把染血剪刀及遺書。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自行攜帶剪刀<br />\n<br />\n醫生搶救發現病人左胸有四處傷口，院方即時通知病人家屬並報警，病人延至當晚11時39分離世。威院發言人表示，個案已呈報死因裁判官跟進。據悉，該把剪刀是病人自行攜帶，並非在醫院拿取。<br />\n<br />\n由於當日病人早已換上病人服，故剪刀較大可能放在隨身行李。該名病人患嚴重肺癌，已在沙田醫院療養一段時間，當日因氣促，轉到威院接受內窺鏡檢查。遺書透露死者因為患病，非常辛苦，故有尋死意向。醫院指對事件感到非常難過，會為家屬提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n急症科醫學院院長蕭粵中表示，左胸是心臟、肺部所在，亦有多條動脈，若遭刺傷，可導致大量出血、心臟短時間內停頓、血胸等嚴重症狀。<br />\n<br />\n他指即使病人在病房內接駁了維生指數監測儀器，在出現嚴重創傷的初期，儀器未必即時發出聲響，要等到脈搏、血壓有較明顯變化時才發聲，故忙於工作的醫護，或未必立即察覺到病人自殘。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民、何家朗  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n路線建議不清晰　運署被轟<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n赴台做咖啡店女僕　港女被捕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:33:16.000Z","msg":"唔洗再做香港人 好事<br />\n祝下世做北歐人"},{"pid":"eac39dd0e976bf2a9ade7f60f57efc1c28bd8985","tid":991103,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"點解佢有勇氣自殺冇勇氣生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n插穿個肺入血水情況同浸死差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bafb40f72be01b5e06eeb6acb164532ba2d2a3c","tid":991103,"uid":118179,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"33e10f02d088fe894029effcf4755479ce936d9f","tid":991103,"uid":147367,"like":152,"dislike":0,"score":152,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:11:58.000Z","msg":"要有幾痛苦先會插到自己四下，仲要忍住唔叫出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"諗起以前有個生Cancer嘅姨姨同我講：化療果啲副作用真係好痛苦，如果佢面前有隻窗佢會毫不猶豫咁跳落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94ffdca3ecb356a4f0e90ab149f986e2c3e1a19","tid":991103,"uid":111006,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"e011b071eb0d82792690a766bfecdc432cdb288a","tid":991103,"uid":28624,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:25:06.000Z","msg":"40歲就有肺癌仲要末期<br />\n<br />\n有可能係死煙產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煙產知道自己下場未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:50:28.0